Package: xrdbi
Title: 'DBI' Backend for 'xarray' via a Live 'reticulate' Session
Version: 0.0.1.9003
Authors@R:
    person("Michael", "Sumner", email = "mdsumner@gmail.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Treats a live Python session holding an 'xarray' object as a
    database connection. Tables are data variables, fields are dimensions
    and coordinates, queries are Python expressions (or compiled from a
    small structured spec) evaluated lazily against the dataset, and
    fetching renders the tidy long-form data frame. The array is a
    rendering format; this package is one veneer over it.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
